imdb.plot outline: Realizing that eccentric job candidates need special care and attention to land jobs, two exes decide to cater to those struggling individuals. There is never a dull moment at their Intimate Temp Agency, where a lot of misfits fight each other to land strange but lucrative temp jobs. Characters include rappers, a prostitute, and a patient member of organized crime. Which candidates will land the temp jobs of their dreams?
